Introduction

Order is important here.  Builders progressively replace stage-1 packages with stage-2 versions.
Stage-2 versions are built from source within nix, using the imported+redirected stage-1 toolchain.

----------------------------------------------------------------
Dependency Tower

Dependencies somewhat overspecified for the sake of simplicity.
(For example nxfs-zlib-2 needs nxfs-sed-2, but not nxfs-gawk-2)

                                 +--------------------------+
                                 | nxfs-glibc-stage1-2      |
                                 +--------------------------+

                                +-------------------+
                                | nxfs-gcc-stage1-2 |
                                +-------------------+


                            +-------------------------------+               +------------+
                            |        nxfs-texinfo-2         |               | nxfs-mpc-2 |
                   +--------+-------------------------------+               +------------+
                   | nxfs-bison-2 |   nxfs-automake-2       |               | nxfs-mpfr-2|
 +-----------------+--------------+-------------------------+---------------+------------+
 | nxfs-binutils-2 | nxfs-flex-2  |   nxfs-autoconf-2       | nxfs-python-2 | nxfs-gmp-2 |
 +--------------------------------+-------------------------+---------------+------------+
 |                  nxfs-perl-2,                            | nxfs-zlib-2   | nxfs-file-2| nxfs-gzip-2,
 |                  nxfs-m4-2                               |               |            | nxfs-patch-2,
 |                                                          |               |            | nxfs-gperf-2
 +----------------------------------------------------------+---------------+------------+
 |                                       nxfs-coreutils-2                                |
 +---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |                                       nxfs-bash-2                                     |
 +---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |                                       nxfs-tar-2                                      |
 +---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |                                       nxfs-gnumake-2                                  |
 +---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
