 +---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |                                   nxfs-gcc-wrapper-2                                  |
 +---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |                                      bootstrap-1                                      |
 +---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


nxfs-gcc-wrapper-2 gcc/g++ wrapper scripts to inject nix-store paths
